Daniel & Team hello,

I am attaching a letter issued by the solicitors handling the sale, which
summarises the terms of the deal.

Exchange and completion are planned for today, with fund transfers to
follow shortly thereafter. Of course, there may be delays to this. The
HSBCPB accounts into which funds will flow are: USD/Capital (for repayment
of the loan mentioned in the letter) and USD/Income (for proceeds of the
sale).

As there is a two-step holdback for 9 and 18 months, not the entire amount
will currently transfer, so please keep this letter as justification for
those later transfers.

Please note:

   1. The exact amounts are subject to completion corrections, but the
   general scope of the deal is correct.
   2. There are two shareholders, so my portion is 50%.

With thanks,

Tamar

--001a11496c5487ee300567d64862
